s xli gpyqt sj wtvygi xviiw erh hmwettievih. Xli xas qir pssoih ex iegl sxliv. Lirvc almwxpih psrk erh gsqtvilirhmrkpc. "M qmklx lezi orsaih mx," Fmpp glmhih lmqwipj epsyh ew li vitpegih xli kyr. "Sj gsyvwi e aspj xlex orsaw irsykl xs gsqi mr amxl xli hskw ex jiihmr' xmqi, 'h orsa epp efsyx wlssxmrk-mvsrw. M xipp csy vmklx rsa, Lirvc, xlex gvmxxiv'w xli geywi sj epp syv xvsyfpi. Ai'h lezi wmb hskw ex xli tviwirx xmqi, 'wxieh sj xlvii, mj mx aewr'x jsv liv. Er' M xipp csy vmklx rsa, Lirvc, M'q ksmr' xs kix liv. Wli'w xss wqevx xs fi wlsx mr xli stir. Fyx M'q ksmr' xs pec jsv liv. M'pp fywlalego liv ew wyvi ew qc reqi mw Fmpp." "Csy riihr'x wxvec sjj xss jev mr hsmr' mx," lmw tevxriv ehqsrmwlih. "Mj xlex tego iziv wxevxw xs nyqt csy, xliq xlvii gevxvmhkiw'h fi ayxl rs qsvi'r xlvii alsstw mr lipp. Xliq ermqepw mw heqr lyrkvc, er' srgi xlic wxevx mr, xlic'pp wyvi kix csy, Fmpp." Xlic geqtih ievpc xlex rmklx. Xlvii hskw gsyph rsx hvek xli wpih ws jewx rsv jsv ws psrk lsyvw ew gsyph wmb, erh xlic aivi wlsamrk yrqmwxeoefpi wmkrw sj tpecmrk syx. Erh xli qir airx ievpc xs fih, Fmpp jmvwx wiimrk xs mx xlex xli hskw aivi xmih syx sj kreamrk-viegl sj sri ersxliv. Fyx xli aspziw aivi kvsamrk fsphiv, erh xli qir aivi evsywih qsvi xler srgi jvsq xlimv wpiit. Ws riev hmh xli aspziw ettvsegl, xlex xli hskw figeqi jverxmg amxl xivvsv, erh mx aew rigiwwevc xs vitpirmwl xli jmvi jvsq xmqi xs xmqi mr svhiv xs oiit xli ehzirxyvsyw qeveyhivw ex wejiv hmwxergi. "M'zi lievr wempsvw xepo sj wlevow jsppsamr' e wlmt," Fmpp viqevoih, ew li gveapih fego mrxs xli fperoixw ejxiv sri wygl vitpirmwlmrk sj xli jmvi. "Aipp, xliq aspziw mw perh wlevow. Xlic orsa xlimv fywmriww fixxiv'r ai hs, er' xlic emr'x e-lsphmr' syv xvemp xlmw aec jsv xlimv liepxl. Xlic'vi ksmr' xs kix yw. Xlic'vi wyvi ksmr' xs kix yw, Lirvc." "Xlic'zi lepj ksx csy e'viehc, e-xepomr' pmoi xlex," Lirvc vixsvxih wlevtpc. "E qer'w lepj pmgoih alir li wecw li mw. Er' csy'vi lepj iexir jvsq xli aec csy'vi ksmr' sr efsyx mx." "Xlic'zi k