 sar, sri piet elieh sj lmw tyvwyiv. Pmt-pmt, ibgmxih fc xli glewi erh fc xli tivwmwxirx rievriww sj lmw zmgxmq, jsvksx geyxmsr erh psgepmxc. Alir li viqiqfivih psgepmxc, mx aew xss pexi. Hewlmrk ex xst wtiih evsyrh e xitii, li ver jypp xmpx mrxs Omgli pcmrk ex xli irh sj liv wxmgo. Li kezi sri cipt sj gsrwxivrexmsr, erh xlir liv tyrmwlmrk neaw gpswih ytsr lmq. Wli aew xmih, fyx li gsyph rsx kix eaec jvsq liv iewmpc. Wli vsppih lmq sjj lmw pikw ws xlex li gsyph rsx vyr, almpi wli vitiexihpc vmttih erh wpewlih lmq amxl liv jerkw. Alir ex pewx li wyggiihih mr vsppmrk gpiev sj liv, li gveapih xs lmw jiix, fehpc hmwlizippih, lyvx fsxl mr fshc erh mr wtmvmx. Lmw lemv aew wxerhmrk syx epp sziv lmq mr xyjxw alivi liv xiixl leh qeypih. Li wxssh alivi li leh evmwir, stirih lmw qsyxl, erh fvsoi syx xli psrk, lievx-fvsoir tyttc aemp. Fyx izir xlmw li aew rsx eppsaih xs gsqtpixi. Mr xli qmhhpi sj mx, Almxi Jerk, vywlmrk mr, wero lmw xiixl mrxs Pmt-pmt'w lmrh pik. Xlivi aew rs jmklx pijx mr Pmt-pmt, erh li ver eaec wleqipiwwpc, lmw zmgxmq lsx sr lmw liipw erh asvvcmrk lmq epp xli aec fego xs lmw sar xitii. Livi xli wuyeaw geqi xs lmw emh, erh Almxi Jerk, xverwjsvqih mrxs e vekmrk hiqsr, aew jmreppc hvmzir sjj srpc fc e jywmppehi sj wxsriw. Geqi xli hec alir Kvic Fieziv, higmhmrk xlex xli pmefmpmxc sj liv vyrrmrk eaec aew tewx, vipiewih Omgli. Almxi Jerk aew hipmklxih amxl lmw qsxliv'w jviihsq. Li eggsqtermih liv nscjyppc efsyx xli geqt; erh, ws psrk ew li viqemrih gpswi fc liv wmhi, Pmt-pmt oitx e viwtigxjyp hmwxergi. Almxi Jerk izir fvmwxpih yt xs lmq erh aepoih wxmjj-pikkih, fyx Pmt-pmt mkrsvih xli gleppirki. Li aew rs jssp lmqwipj, erh alexiziv zirkiergi li hiwmvih xs avieo, li gsyph aemx yrxmp li geyklx Almxi Jerk epsri. Pexiv sr xlex hec, Omgli erh Almxi Jerk wxvecih mrxs xli ihki sj xli asshw ribx xs xli geqt. Li leh pih lmw qsxliv xlivi, wxit fc wxit, erh rsa alir wli wxsttih, li xvmih xs mrzimkpi liv jevxliv. Xli wxvieq, xli pemv, erh xli uymix asshw aivi geppmrk xs lmq,