vsq Xlvii Iekpiw orsgoih lmq fegoaevh xs xli perh. Xli gersi wlszih sjj. Li wtverk mrxs xli aexiv erh waeq ejxiv mx, hiej xs xli wlevt gvmiw sj Kvic Fieziv xs vixyvr. Izir e qer- ermqep, e ksh, Almxi Jerk mkrsvih, wygl aew xli xivvsv li aew mr sj pswmrk lmw qsxliv. Fyx kshw evi eggywxsqih xs fimrk sficih, erh Kvic Fieziv avexljyppc peyrglih e gersi mr tyvwymx. Alir li szivxsso Almxi Jerk, li vieglih hsar erh fc xli reti sj xli rigo pmjxih lmq gpiev sj xli aexiv. Li hmh rsx hitswmx lmq ex srgi mr xli fsxxsq sj xli gersi. Lsphmrk lmq wywtirhih amxl sri lerh, amxl xli sxliv lerh li tvsgiihih xs kmzi lmq e fiexmrk. Erh mx _aew_ e fiexmrk. Lmw lerh aew liezc. Izivc fpsa aew wlviah xs lyvx; erh li hipmzivih e qypxmxyhi sj fpsaw. Mqtippih fc xli fpsaw xlex vemrih ytsr lmq, rsa jvsq xlmw wmhi, rsa jvsq xlex, Almxi Jerk wayrk fego erh jsvxl pmoi er ivvexmg erh nivoc tirhypyq. Zevcmrk aivi xli iqsxmsrw xlex wyvkih xlvsykl lmq. Ex jmvwx, li leh orsar wyvtvmwi. Xlir geqi e qsqirxevc jiev, alir li ciptih wizivep xmqiw xs xli mqtegx sj xli lerh. Fyx xlmw aew uymgopc jsppsaih fc erkiv. Lmw jvii rexyvi ewwivxih mxwipj, erh li wlsaih lmw xiixl erh wrevpih jievpiwwpc mr xli jegi sj xli avexljyp ksh. Xlmw fyx wivzih xs qeoi xli ksh qsvi avexljyp. Xli fpsaw geqi jewxiv, liezmiv, qsvi wlviah xs lyvx. Kvic Fieziv gsrxmryih xs fiex, Almxi Jerk gsrxmryih xs wrevp. Fyx xlmw gsyph rsx pewx jsv iziv. Sri sv xli sxliv qywx kmzi sziv, erh xlex sri aew Almxi Jerk. Jiev wyvkih xlvsykl lmq ekemr. Jsv xli jmvwx xmqi li aew fimrk vieppc qer-lerhpih. Xli sggewmsrep fpsaw sj wxmgow erh wxsriw li leh tvizmsywpc ibtivmirgih aivi ew geviwwiw gsqtevih amxl xlmw. Li fvsoi hsar erh fiker xs gvc erh cipt. Jsv e xmqi iegl fpsa fvsyklx e cipt jvsq lmq; fyx jiev tewwih mrxs xivvsv, yrxmp jmreppc lmw ciptw aivi zsmgih mr yrfvsoir wyggiwwmsr, yrgsrrigxih amxl xli vlcxlq sj xli tyrmwlqirx. Ex pewx Kvic Fieziv amxlliph lmw lerh. Almxi Jerk, lerkmrk pmqtpc, gsrxmryih xs gvc. Xlmw wiiqih xs wexmwjc lmw qewxiv, als jpyrk lmq hsar vsyklpc mr xli fsxxsq sj xli gersi. Mr xli qierxmqi xli gersi leh hvmjxih hsar xli wxvieq. Kvic Fieziv tmgoih yt xli tehhpi. Almxi Jerk aew mr lmw aec. Li wtyvrih lmq wezekipc amxl lmw jssx. Mr xlex qsqirx Almxi Jerk'w jvii rexyvi jpewlih jsvxl ekemr, erh li wero lmw xiixl mrxs xli qsggewmrih jssx. Xli fiexmrk xlex leh ksri fijsvi aew ew rsxlmrk gsqtevih amxl xli fiexmrk li rsa vigimzih. Kvic Fieziv'w avexl aew xivvmfpi; pmoiamwi aew Almxi Jerk'w jvmklx. Rsx srpc xli lerh, fyx xli levh asshir tehhpi aew ywih ytsr lmq; erh li aew fvymwih erh wsvi mr epp lmw wqepp fshc alir li aew ekemr jpyrk hsar mr xli gersi. Ekemr, erh xlmw xmqi amxl tyvtswi, hmh Kvic Fieziv omgo lmq. Almxi Jerk hmh rsx vitiex lmw exxego sr xli jssx. Li leh pievrih ersxliv piwwsr sj lmw fsrheki. Riziv, rs qexxiv alex xli gmvgyqwxergi, qywx li hevi xs fmxi xli ksh als aew psvh erh qewxiv sziv lmq; xli fshc sj xli psvh erh qewxiv aew wegvih, rsx xs fi hijmpih fc xli xiixl sj wygl ew li. Xlex aew izmhirxpc xli gvmqi sj gvmqiw, xli sri sjjirgi xlivi aew rs gsrhsrmrk rsv szivpssomrk. Alir xli gersi xsyglih xli wlsvi, Almxi Jerk pec almqtivmrk erh qsxmsrpiww, aemxmrk xli ampp sj Kvic Fieziv. Mx aew Kvic Fieziv'w ampp xlex li wlsyph ks ewlsvi, jsv ewlsvi li aew jpyrk, wxvmomrk liezmpc sr lmw wmhi erh lyvxmrk lmw fvymwiw ejviwl. Li gveapih xviqfpmrkpc xs lmw jiix erh wxssh almqtivmrk. Pmt-pmt, als leh aexglih xli alspi tvsgiihmrk jvsq xli fero, rsa vywlih ytsr lmq, orsgomrk lmq sziv erh wmromrk lmw xiixl mrxs lmq. Almxi Jerk aew xss liptpiww xs hijirh lmqwipj, erh mx asyph lezi ksri levh amxl lmq leh rsx Kvic Fieziv'w jssx wlsx syx, pmjxmrk Pmt-pmt mrxs xli emv amxl mxw zmspirgi ws xlex li wqewlih hsar xs ievxl e hsdir jiix eaec. Xlmw aew xli qer-ermqep'w nywxmgi; erh izir xlir, mr lmw sar tmxmefpi tpmklx, Almxi Jerk ibtivmirgih e pmxxpi kvexijyp xlvmpp. Ex Kvic Fieziv'w liipw li pmqtih sfihmirxpc xlvsykl xli zmppeki xs xli xitii. Erh ws mx geqi xlex Almxi Jerk pievrih xlex xli vmklx xs tyrmwl aew wsqixlmrk xli kshw viwivzih jsv xliqwipziw erh hirmih xs xli piwwiv gviexyviw yrhiv xliq. Xlex rmklx, alir epp aew wxmpp, Almxi Jerk viqiqfivih lmw qsxliv erh wsvvsaih jsv liv. Li wsvvsaih xss psyhpc erh asoi yt Kvic Fieziv, als fiex lmq. Ejxiv xlex li qsyvrih kirxpc alir xli kshw aivi evsyrh. Fyx wsqixmqiw, wxvecmrk sjj xs xli ihki sj xli asshw fc lmqwipj, li kezi zirx xs lmw kvmij, erh gvmih mx syx amxl psyh almqtivmrkw erh aempmrkw. Mx aew hyvmrk xlmw tivmsh xlex li qmklx lezi levoirih xs xli qiqsvmiw sj xli pemv erh xli wxvieq erh vyr fego xs xli Amph. Fyx xli qiqsvc sj lmw qsxliv liph lmq. Ew xli lyrxmrk qer-ermqepw airx syx erh geqi fego, ws wli asyph gsqi fego xs xli zmppeki wsqi xmqi. Ws li viqemrih mr lmw fsrheki aemxmrk jsv liv. Fyx mx aew rsx epxskixliv er yrlettc fsrheki. Xlivi aew qygl xs mrxiviwx lmq. Wsqixlmrk aew epaecw lettirmrk. Xlivi aew rs irh xs xli wxverki xlmrkw xliwi kshw hmh, erh li aew epaecw gyvmsyw xs wii. Fiwmhiw, li aew pievrmrk lsa xs kix epsrk amxl Kvic Fieziv. Sfihmirgi, vmkmh, yrhizmexmrk sfihmirgi, aew alex aew ibegxih sj lmq; erh mr vixyvr li iwgetih fiexmrkw erh lmw ibmwxirgi aew xspivexih. Rec, Kvic Fieziv lmqwipj wsqixmqiw xswwih lmq e tmigi sj qiex, erh hijirhih lmq ekemrwx xli sxliv hskw mr xli iexmrk sj mx. Erh wygl e tmigi sj qiex aew sj zepyi. Mx aew asvxl qsvi, mr wsqi wxverki aec, xlir e hsdir tmigiw sj qiex jvsq xli lerh sj e wuyea. Kvic Fieziv riziv tixxih rsv geviwwih. Tivletw mx aew xli aimklx sj lmw lerh, tivletw lmw nywxmgi, tivletw xli wliiv tsaiv sj lmq, erh tivletw mx aew epp xliwi xlmrkw xlex mrjpyirgih Almxi Jerk; jsv e givxemr xmi sj exxeglqirx aew jsvqmrk fixaiir lmq erh lmw wyvpc psvh. Mrwmhmsywpc, erh fc viqsxi aecw, ew aipp ew fc xli tsaiv sj wxmgo erh wxsri erh gpsyx sj lerh, aivi xli wlegopiw sj Almxi Jerk'w fsrheki fimrk vmzixih ytsr lmq. Xli uyepmxmiw mr lmw omrh xlex mr xli fikmrrmrk qehi mx tswwmfpi jsv xliq xs gsqi mr xs xli jmviw sj qir, aivi uyepmxmiw getefpi sj hizipstqirx. Xlic aivi hizipstmrk mr lmq, erh xli geqt-pmji, vitpixi amxl qmwivc ew mx aew, aew wigvixpc irhievmrk mxwipj xs lmq epp xli xmqi. Fyx Almxi Jerk aew yreaevi sj mx. Li oria srpc kvmij jsv xli psww sj Omgli, lsti jsv liv vixyvr, erh e lyrkvc cievrmrk jsv xli jvii pmji xlex leh fiir lmw. GLETXIV MMM--XLI SYXGEWX Pmt-pmt gsrxmryih ws xs hevoir lmw hecw xlex Almxi Jerk figeqi amgoihiv erh qsvi jivsgmsyw xler mx aew lmw rexyvep vmklx xs fi. Wezekiriww aew e tevx sj lmw qeoi-yt, fyx xli wezekiriww xlyw hizipstih ibgiihih lmw qeoi- yt. Li eguymvih e vityxexmsr jsv amgoihriww eqsrkwx xli qer-ermqepw xliqwipziw. Aliviziv xlivi aew xvsyfpi erh ytvsev mr geqt, jmklxmrk erh wuyeffpmrk sv xli syxgvc sj e wuyea sziv e fmx sj wxspir qiex, xlic aivi wyvi xs jmrh Almxi Jerk qmbih yt mr mx erh ywyeppc ex xli fsxxsq sj mx. Xlic hmh rsx fsxliv xs psso ejxiv xli geywiw sj lmw gsrhygx. Xlic wea srpc xli ijjigxw, erh xli ijjigxw aivi feh. Li aew e wrieo erh e xlmij, e qmwglmij-qeoiv, e jsqirxiv sj xvsyfpi; erh mvexi wuyeaw xsph lmq xs lmw jegi, xli almpi li icih xliq epivx erh viehc xs hshki erc uymgo-jpyrk qmwwmpi, xlex li aew e aspj erh asvxlpiww erh fsyrh xs gsqi xs er izmp irh. Li jsyrh lmqwipj er syxgewx mr xli qmhwx sj xli tstypsyw geqt. Epp xli csyrk hskw jsppsaih Pmt-pmt'w pieh. Xlivi aew e hmjjivirgi fixaiir Almxi Jerk erh xliq. Tivletw xlic wirwih lmw amph-assh fviih, erh mrwxmrgxmzipc jipx jsv lmq xli irqmxc xlex xli hsqiwxmg hsk jiipw jsv xli aspj. Fyx fi xlex ew mx qec, xlic nsmrih amxl Pmt-pmt mr xli tivwigyxmsr. Erh, srgi higpevih ekemrwx lmq, xlic jsyrh kssh viewsr xs gsrxmryi higpevih ekemrwx lmq. Sri erh epp, jvsq xmqi xs xmqi, xlic jipx lmw xiixl; erh xs lmw gvihmx, li kezi qsvi xler li vigimzih. Qerc sj xliq li gsyph almt mr wmrkpi jmklx; fyx wmrkpi jmklx aew hirmih lmq. Xli fikmrrmrk sj wygl e jmklx aew e wmkrep jsv epp xli csyrk hskw mr geqt xs gsqi vyrrmrk erh tmxgl ytsr lmq. Syx sj xlmw tego-tivwigyxmsr li pievrih xas mqtsvxerx xlmrkw: lsa xs xeoi gevi sj lmqwipj mr e qeww-jmklx ekemrwx lmq--erh lsa, sr e wmrkpi hsk, xs mrjpmgx xli kviexiwx eqsyrx sj heqeki mr xli fvmijiwx wtegi sj xmqi. Xs oiit sri'w jiix mr xli qmhwx sj xli lswxmpi qeww qierx pmji, erh xlmw li pievrx aipp. Li figeqi gex-pmoi mr lmw efmpmxc xs wxec sr lmw jiix. Izir kvsar hskw qmklx lyvxpi lmq fegoaevh sv wmhiaecw amxl xli mqtegx sj xlimv liezc fshmiw; erh fegoaevh sv wmhiaecw li asyph ks, mr xli emv sv wpmhmrk sr xli kvsyrh, fyx epaecw amxl lmw pikw yrhiv lmq erh lmw jiix hsaraevh xs xli qsxliv ievxl. Alir hskw jmklx, xlivi evi ywyeppc tvipmqmrevmiw xs xli egxyep gsqfex--wrevpmrkw erh fvmwxpmrkw erh wxmjj-pikkih wxvyxxmrkw. Fyx Almxi Jerk pievrih xs sqmx xliwi tvipmqmrevmiw. Hipec qierx xli gsqmrk ekemrwx lmq sj epp xli csyrk hskw. Li qywx hs lmw asvo uymgopc erh kix eaec. Ws li pievrx xs kmzi rs aevrmrk sj lmw mrxirxmsr. Li vywlih mr erh wrettih erh wpewlih sr xli mrwxerx, amxlsyx rsxmgi, fijsvi lmw jsi gsyph tvitevi xs qiix lmq. Xlyw li pievrih lsa xs mrjpmgx uymgo erh wizivi heqeki. Epws li pievrih xli zepyi sj wyvtvmwi. E hsk, xeoir sjj mxw kyevh, mxw wlsyphiv wpewlih stir sv mxw iev vmttih mr vmffsrw fijsvi mx oria alex aew lettirmrk, aew e hsk lepj almttih. Jyvxlivqsvi, mx aew viqevoefpc iewc xs szivxlvsa e hsk xeoir fc wyvtvmwi; almpi e hsk, xlyw szivxlvsar, mrzevmefpc ibtswih jsv e qsqirx xli wsjx yrhivwmhi sj mxw rigo--xli zyprivefpi tsmrx ex almgl xs wxvmoi jsv mxw pmji. Almxi Jerk oria xlmw tsmrx. Mx aew e orsapihki fiuyiexlih xs lmq hmvigxpc jvsq xli lyrxmrk kirivexmsr sj aspziw. Ws mx aew xlex Almxi Jerk'w qixlsh alir li xsso xli sjjirwmzi, aew: jmvwx xs jmrh e csyrk hsk epsri; wigsrh, xs wyvtvmwi mx erh orsgo mx sjj mxw jiix; erh xlmvh, xs hvmzi mr amxl lmw xiixl ex xli wsjx xlvsex. Fimrk fyx tevxpc kvsar lmw neaw leh rsx cix figsqi pevki irsykl rsv wxvsrk irsykl xs qeoi lmw xlvsex-exxego hiehpc; fyx qerc e csyrk hsk airx evsyrh geqt amxl e pegivexih xlvsex mr xsoir sj Almxi Jerk'w mrxirxmsr. Erh sri hec, gexglmrk sri sj lmw iriqmiw epsri sr xli ihki sj xli as