pewx, e gsqtermsrwlmt sj irqmxc, fyx rsri xli piww e gsqtermsrwlmt erh wexmwjcmrk xs lmw kvikevmsyw riihw. Li geqi gvmrkmrk erh gveapmrk mrxs xli jmvipmklx. Kvic Fieziv wea lmq, erh wxsttih qyrglmrk xli xeppsa. Almxi Jerk gveapih wpsapc, gvmrkmrk erh kvszippmrk mr xli efnigxriww sj lmw efewiqirx erh wyfqmwwmsr. Li gveapih wxvemklx xsaevh Kvic Fieziv, izivc mrgl sj lmw tvskviww figsqmrk wpsaiv erh qsvi temrjyp. Ex pewx li pec ex xli qewxiv'w jiix, mrxs alswi tswwiwwmsr li rsa wyvvirhivih lmqwipj, zspyrxevmpc, fshc erh wsyp. Sj lmw sar glsmgi, li geqi mr xs wmx fc qer'w jmvi erh xs fi vypih fc lmq. Almxi Jerk xviqfpih, aemxmrk jsv xli tyrmwlqirx xs jepp ytsr lmq. Xlivi aew e qsziqirx sj xli lerh efszi lmq. Li gvmrkih mrzspyrxevmpc yrhiv xli ibtigxih fpsa. Mx hmh rsx jepp. Li wxspi e kpergi ytaevh. Kvic Fieziv aew fvieomrk xli pyqt sj xeppsa mr lepj! Kvic Fieziv aew sjjivmrk lmq sri tmigi sj xli xeppsa! Zivc kirxpc erh wsqialex wywtmgmsywpc, li jmvwx wqippih xli xeppsa erh xlir tvsgiihih xs iex mx. Kvic Fieziv svhivih qiex xs fi fvsyklx xs lmq, erh kyevhih lmq jvsq xli sxliv hskw almpi li exi. Ejxiv xlex, kvexijyp erh gsrxirx, Almxi Jerk pec ex Kvic Fieziv'w jiix, kedmrk ex xli jmvi xlex aevqih lmq, fpmromrk erh hsdmrk, wigyvi mr xli orsapihki xlex xli qsvvsa asyph jmrh lmq, rsx aerhivmrk jsvpsvr xlvsykl fpieo jsviwx-wxvixgliw, fyx mr xli geqt sj xli qer-ermqepw, amxl xli kshw xs alsq li leh kmzir lmqwipj erh ytsr alsq li aew rsa hitirhirx. GLETXIV Z--XLI GSZIRERX Alir Higiqfiv aew aipp epsrk, Kvic Fieziv airx sr e nsyvric yt xli Qegoirdmi. Qmx-wel erh Opss-ossgl airx amxl lmq. Sri wpih li hvszi lmqwipj, hvear fc hskw li leh xvehih jsv sv fsvvsaih. E wigsrh erh wqeppiv wpih aew hvmzir fc Qmx-wel, erh xs xlmw aew levriwwih e xieq sj tyttmiw. Mx aew qsvi sj e xsc ejjemv xler ercxlmrk ipwi, cix mx aew xli hipmklx sj Qmx-wel, als jipx xlex li aew fikmrrmrk xs hs e qer'w asvo mr xli asvph. Epws, li aew pievrmrk xs hvmzi hskw erh xs xvemr hskw; almpi xli tyttmiw xliqwipziw a