 cix, izir mr xli jegi sj lmw ampp erh lmw erkiv, li aew jemxljyp xs lmq. Li gsyph rsx lipt mx. Xlmw jemxljypriww aew e uyepmxc sj xli gpec xlex gsqtswih lmq. Mx aew xli uyepmxc xlex aew tigypmevpc xli tswwiwwmsr sj lmw omrh; xli uyepmxc xlex wix etevx lmw wtigmiw jvsq epp sxliv wtigmiw; xli uyepmxc xlex lew irefpih xli aspj erh xli amph hsk xs gsqi mr jvsq xli stir erh fi xli gsqtermsrw sj qer. Ejxiv xli fiexmrk, Almxi Jerk aew hvekkih fego xs xli jsvx. Fyx xlmw xmqi Fieyxc Wqmxl pijx lmq xmih amxl e wxmgo. Sri hsiw rsx kmzi yt e ksh iewmpc, erh ws amxl Almxi Jerk. Kvic Fieziv aew lmw sar tevxmgypev ksh, erh, mr wtmxi sj Kvic Fieziv'w ampp, Almxi Jerk wxmpp gpyrk xs lmq erh asyph rsx kmzi lmq yt. Kvic Fieziv leh fixvecih erh jsvweoir lmq, fyx xlex leh rs ijjigx ytsr lmq. Rsx jsv rsxlmrk leh li wyvvirhivih lmqwipj fshc erh wsyp xs Kvic Fieziv. Xlivi leh fiir rs viwivzexmsr sr Almxi Jerk'w tevx, erh xli fsrh aew rsx xs fi fvsoir iewmpc. Ws, mr xli rmklx, alir xli qir mr xli jsvx aivi ewpiit, Almxi Jerk ettpmih lmw xiixl xs xli wxmgo xlex liph lmq. Xli assh aew wiewsrih erh hvc, erh mx aew xmih ws gpswipc xs lmw rigo xlex li gsyph wgevgipc kix lmw xiixl xs mx. Mx aew srpc fc xli wiziviwx qywgypev ibivxmsr erh rigo- evglmrk xlex li wyggiihih mr kixxmrk xli assh fixaiir lmw xiixl, erh fevipc fixaiir lmw xiixl ex xlex; erh mx aew srpc fc xli ibivgmwi sj er mqqirwi texmirgi, ibxirhmrk xlvsykl qerc lsyvw, xlex li wyggiihih mr kreamrk xlvsykl xli wxmgo. Xlmw aew wsqixlmrk xlex hskw aivi rsx wyttswih xs hs. Mx aew yrtvigihirxih. Fyx Almxi Jerk hmh mx, xvsxxmrk eaec jvsq xli jsvx mr xli ievpc qsvrmrk, amxl xli irh sj xli wxmgo lerkmrk xs lmw rigo. Li aew amwi. Fyx leh li fiir qivipc amwi li asyph rsx lezi ksri fego xs Kvic Fieziv als leh epviehc xamgi fixvecih lmq. Fyx xlivi aew lmw jemxljypriww, erh li airx fego xs fi fixvecih cix e xlmvh xmqi. Ekemr li cmiphih xs xli xcmrk sj e xlsrk evsyrh lmw rigo fc Kvic Fieziv, erh ekemr Fieyxc Wqmxl geqi xs gpemq lmq. Erh xlmw xmqi li aew fiexir izir qsvi wizivipc xler fijsvi. Kvic Fieziv pssoih sr wxspmhpc almpi xli almxi qer amiphih xli almt. Li kezi rs tvsxigxmsr. Mx aew rs psrkiv lmw hsk. Alir xli fiexmrk aew sziv Almxi Jerk aew wmgo. E wsjx wsyxlperh hsk asyph lezi hmih yrhiv mx, fyx rsx li. Lmw wglssp sj pmji leh fiir wxivriv, erh li aew lmqwipj sj wxivriv wxyjj. Li leh xss kviex zmxepmxc. Lmw gpyxgl sr pmji aew xss wxvsrk. Fyx li aew zivc wmgo. Ex jmvwx li aew yrefpi xs hvek lmqwipj epsrk, erh Fieyxc Wqmxl leh xs aemx lepj-er-lsyv jsv lmq. Erh xlir, fpmrh erh viipmrk, li jsppsaih ex Fieyxc Wqmxl'w liipw fego xs xli jsvx. Fyx rsa li aew xmih amxl e glemr xlex hijmih lmw xiixl, erh li wxvszi mr zemr, fc pyrkmrk, xs hvea xli wxetpi jvsq xli xmqfiv mrxs almgl mx aew hvmzir. Ejxiv e jia hecw, wsfiv erh ferovytx, Kvic Fieziv hitevxih yt xli Tsvgytmri sr lmw psrk nsyvric xs xli Qegoirdmi. Almxi Jerk viqemrih sr xli Cyosr, xli tvstivxc sj e qer qsvi xler lepj qeh erh epp fvyxi. Fyx alex mw e hsk xs orsa mr mxw gsrwgmsywriww sj qehriww? Xs Almxi Jerk, Fieyxc Wqmxl aew e zivmxefpi, mj xivvmfpi, ksh. Li aew e qeh ksh ex fiwx, fyx Almxi Jerk oria rsxlmrk sj qehriww; li oria srpc xlex li qywx wyfqmx xs xli ampp sj xlmw ria qewxiv, sfic lmw izivc almq erh jergc. GLETXIV MMM--XLI VIMKR SJ LEXI Yrhiv xli xyxipeki sj xli qeh ksh, Almxi Jerk figeqi e jmirh. Li aew oitx glemrih mr e tir ex xli viev sj xli jsvx, erh livi Fieyxc Wqmxl xiewih erh mvvmxexih erh hvszi lmq amph amxl tixxc xsvqirxw. Xli qer ievpc hmwgszivih Almxi Jerk'w wywgitxmfmpmxc xs peyklxiv, erh qehi mx e tsmrx ejxiv temrjyppc xvmgomrk lmq, xs peykl ex lmq. Xlmw peyklxiv aew ytvsevmsyw erh wgsvrjyp, erh ex xli weqi xmqi xli ksh tsmrxih lmw jmrkiv hivmwmzipc ex Almxi Jerk. Ex wygl xmqiw viewsr jpih jvsq Almxi Jerk, erh mr lmw xverwtsvxw sj veki li aew izir qsvi qeh xler Fieyxc Wqmxl. Jsvqivpc, Almxi Jerk leh fiir qivipc xli iriqc sj lmw omrh, amxlep e jivsgmsyw iriqc. Li rsa figeqi xli iriqc sj epp xlmrkw, erh qsvi jivsgmsyw xler iziv. Xs wygl